  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00187', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-111-4b605adb', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-03', NULL, 'essay', '甲為發明專利案 A 之專利權人，該發明專利案 A 係援引日本公司乙所
